This is the README file for Acme::Comment by Jos Boumans.

Please type "perldoc Acme::Comment" after installation to see the
module usage information. 

----------------------------------------------------------------------

* Installation

Acme::Comment uses the standard perl module install process:

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

